Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}Corra, corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:06.46,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Erguendo bem alto sua bandeira aos céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:18.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos cruzar este mar sem fim 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,em busca do milagre que 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.94,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,ninguém ainda encontrou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:27.96,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Avançaremos seguindo os desejos de nossos corações pulsantes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.71,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,seguindo as pegadas daqueles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:35.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,que perseguem seus sonhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Por mais tormentuosa que seja a noite,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,se unirmos nossos corações,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:46.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}nós vamos superá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.86,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Corra, corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.55,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}Erguendo bem alto sua bandeira aos céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:57.14,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mesmo se rolarem lágrimas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:00.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}que ninguém mais verá
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.52,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Persiga, persiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:06.52,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,o sonho indicado pela bússola,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:09.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,olhando sempre em frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:14.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}Não podemos parar a volta ao mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}Me incendeie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.49,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Corra, corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:24.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Chegue mais longe que todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se não desviarmos de nossa rota,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}o amanhã estará em nossas mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Persiga, persiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:36.51,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,que tudo que vemos diante de nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.93,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos escrever nas páginas em branco...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.43,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,em nossos corações!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:46.43,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Admirável Mundo Novo, me incendeie!

