Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.31,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Get running, get running
Comment: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.40,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,holding our flag high in the sky
Comment: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:17.99,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of
Comment: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.75,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,a global miracle no one
Comment: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.83,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,has yet been able to find
Comment: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.92,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,With our hearts pounding,
Comment: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.71,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,we'll just charge ahead as we please following
Comment: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:35.59,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,the footprints of those who chase their dreams
Comment: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.39,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,No matter how stormy the night,
Comment: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.35,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,if we join our hearts as one
Comment: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.52,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,we will be able to make it through
Comment: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:47.77,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,always
Comment: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.57,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Get running, get running
Comment: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.53,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,holding our flag high in the sky
Comment: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.07,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Even though there are tears
Comment: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.49,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,we don't want anyone to see
Comment: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.45,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Chase it, chase it,
Comment: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.46,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,if you want to achieve our dream we should
Comment: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.13,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,always look straight ahead without fear
Comment: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.38,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,We can't stop here
Comment: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.43,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Get running, get running,
Comment: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:24.48,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,head past everyone else
Comment: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.06,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,So long as we don't run from it,
Comment: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.48,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(0,30)}we can grasp tomorrow in our hands
Comment: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.57,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,Chase it, chase it,
Comment: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.49,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,everything we see before us,
Comment: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.86,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,let's carve it into the
Comment: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.37,Translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,blank pages of our hearts
